    AdobeBehanceSearchProjectOptions represents the options for creating search query to search published Behance Projects. This class provides the following set of options(mentioned below) for creating search query to search published Behance Projects.
    • Page Number - retrieves the projects from the given result page number.
    • Search String - retrieves the projects based on the given search string.
    • Field - retrieves the projects tagged with the given creative field.
    • Sort Option - retrieves the projects sorted on one of these params : FEATURED_DATE, APPRECIATIONS, VIEWS, COMMENTS, PUBLISHED_DATE, RELEVANCE.
    • TimeSpan - retrieves the projects belonging to one of these time-period : ALL,MONTH,WEEK or TODAY.
    • Country - retrieves the projects associated with this country.
    • State - retrieves the projects associated with the given state.
    • City - retrieves the projects associated with the given city.
    • Tags - retrieves the projects associated with the given tags.
